data.message: How boring could live life just existing! You have to do something to make this world a better world. Leave your mark in the world and you will be unforgettable. By living a life of service ,morals,ethics and with a lot of love and compassion towards others. By just existing you're not following your heart, you're not living your dream. We were placed in this world To co- create beautiful and loving things and leave a positive loving imprint in the lives and heats of the peopke that crossed in your journey throughout your life.
Very well said Susan M. Garcia such beautiful lines.
